 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner-tomb-raider@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner-tomb-raider@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner-tomb-raider@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <em>《权力的游戏》</em>明星索菲·特纳正在就领导<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Amazon Prime Video</a>即将推出的<em>《古墓丽影</em>r》系列进行谈判。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="570" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tomb-raider-at-25-ian-livingstone-talks-about-the-birth-of-lara-croft-3084441"><b>25 岁的《古墓丽影》——伊恩·利文斯通 (Ian Livingstone) 谈论劳拉·克劳馥 (Lara Croft) 的诞生</b></a></li></ul><p>5 月，Amazon Prime Video 和 Amazon MGM Studios 宣布与视频游戏开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/crystal-dynamics">Crystal Dynamics</a>合作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/phoebe-waller-bridge-to-write-tomb-raider-series-for-prime-video-3756342">开发新的<i>《古墓丽影》</i>系列</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-waller-bridge">菲比·沃勒-布里奇</a>将担任该剧的编剧和监制。</p><p>现在，根据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/11/sophie-turner-lara-croft-tomb-raider-phoebe-waller-bridge-amazon-1236173978/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline 的</em></a>报道，特纳正在积极谈判，以饰演主角劳拉·克劳馥（Lara Croft）。如果特纳获得这个角色，她将成为第三个在真人场景中将这个角色演绎得栩栩如生的人。安吉丽娜·朱莉 (Angelina Jolie) 于 2000 年代初在两部<em>《古墓丽影》(Tomb Raider)</em>电影中首次扮演该角色，随后艾丽西亚·维坎德 (Alicia Vikander) 于 2018 年出演。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807998" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807998" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807998" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="索菲·特纳" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2024_sophieturner_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807998" class="wp-caption-text">索菲·特纳 (Sophie Turner) 出席 2024 年 9 月 19 日在伦敦杰克·所罗门俱乐部举行的独立电视台新剧集《琼》的发布会 图片来源：James Manning/PA Images via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>目前，有关沃勒-布里奇改编的细节尚未透露。</p><p>沃勒-布里奇此前谈到她参与该剧时说道：“如果我能告诉我十几岁的自己，这件事正在发生，我想她会爆炸。 <em>《古墓丽影》</em>已经成为我生活中很重要的一部分，能够与如此热情的合作者将其搬上电视，我感到非常荣幸。劳拉·克劳馥对我来说意义重大，就像她对许多人一样，我迫不及待地想继续这次冒险。都是蝙蝠。”</p><p>特纳可能参与该剧的可能性<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/game-of-thrones-star-sophie-turner-up-for-lara-croft-role-in-new-tomb-raider-tv-series-3807929">于十月份首次被报道</a>，当时有消息称她是参加该角色试镜的演员之一。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812949" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812949" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812949" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sophie-turner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812949" class="wp-caption-text">苏菲·特纳。图片来源：Marc Piasecki/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>在个人方面，特纳最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sophie-turner-says-joe-jonas-split-worst-few-days-of-life-3756786">公开了她</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joe-jonas">乔乔纳斯</a>离婚的事情。这对已经在一起八年、结婚四年的前夫妇<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/joe-jonas-sophie-turner-confirm-split-four-years-marriage-3494169">于 2023 年宣布分居</a>。</p><p>去年10月，两人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-jonas-and-sophie-turner-reach-amicable-resolution-in-custody-battle-3512880">在监护权之争中达成了“友好解决方案”</a> ，同意孩子们“将在美国和英国充满爱的家庭中平等地度过时光”。特纳目前正在 ITVX 主演英国犯罪剧限定剧<em>《琼》</em> 。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a>动漫系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tomb-raider"><i>《古墓丽影：劳拉·克劳馥传奇》</i></a>于 10 月首播，这个传奇人物由海莉·阿特维尔配音。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/tomb-raider-sophie-turner-reportedly-in-negotiations-to-play-lara-croft-3812944">《古墓丽影》后报道：据报道，索菲·特纳 (Sophie Turner) 正在洽谈扮演劳拉·克劳馥 (Lara Croft)，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
大卫·林奇现在需要补充氧气才能行走：“这是一个很大的代价” https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-now-requires-supplemental-oxygen-to-walk-its-a-big-price-to-pay-3812940?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=大卫·林奇现在需要补充氧气才能行走，这是一个巨大的代价Surej SinghFri, 15 Nov 2024 05:28:53 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3812940 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>八岁开始吸烟的导演2020年被诊断患有肺气肿</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-now-requires-supplemental-oxygen-to-walk-its-a-big-price-to-pay-3812940">大卫·林奇现在需要补充氧气才能行走：“这是一个巨大的代价”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/david-lynch@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">大卫·林奇</a>分享了他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-health-problems-mean-he-can-no-longer-direct-in-person-3781105">肺气肿诊断</a>的最新情况，透露他现在需要补充氧气才能行走——看看这位受人尊敬的电影制作人在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/twin-peaks-season-4-lynch-future-2147468">《双峰》的未来：会有第四季吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p>林奇从 8 岁起就开始吸烟，并于 2020 年被诊断出患有肺气肿。从那时起，他就只能待在家里，因为这种情况严重影响了他的免疫系统。</p><p>在与<a href="https://people.com/david-lynch-smoking-at-age-8-now-he-needs-oxygen-copd-exclusive-8743594"><em>《人物》杂志的</em></a>一次新的聊天中，林奇分享了他的最新病情，并表示尽管两年前已经戒烟，但如果他做任何剧烈的事情，他都需要额外的氧气——即使是走过一个房间也会让他喘不过气来。</p><p>他告诉该出版物：“我对身体康复本身抱有积极的态度。患有肺气肿的生活很艰难。我几乎无法穿过一个房间。就像你头上套着一个塑料袋到处走动一样。” </p><figure id="attachment_3762766" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762766" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762766" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project.jpg" alt="大卫·林奇" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/David-Lynch-new-project-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762766" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·林奇于 2019 年 9 月 19 日在加利福尼亚州比佛利山庄。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Michael Kovac/FilmMagic for AFI</figcaption></figure><p>尽管他的病情“付出了巨大的代价”，林奇说：“我并不后悔。这对我来说很重要。我希望每个瘾君子都希望：我们所爱的东西对我们有好处。我从来没有想过它是为了美化它。这是生活的一部分。有些角色会抽烟，就像现实生活中一样。”</p><p>虽然他并不后悔吸烟，但他希望其他吸烟者能够以他为榜样：“我真的很想让大家明白这一点：想一想。你可以戒掉这些最终会杀死你的事情。我应该对他们——以及我自己——说出这样的话。”</p><p>肺气肿，也称为慢性阻塞性肺病 (COPD)，是指由于吸烟、污染或工作场所刺激物（根据<a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/chronic-obstructive-pulmonary-disease-copd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>NHS</i></a> ）而导致的肺泡损伤。这种疾病会导致呼吸问题、咳嗽，患有这种疾病的人可能会频繁出现胸部感染和喘息。</p><p>林奇<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-health-problems-mean-he-can-no-longer-direct-in-person-3781105">在八月解释这种情况对他的影响时</a>说：“我因长期吸烟而患上肺气肿，所以无论我喜欢与否，我都待在家里。即使是感冒，生病对我来说也是非常糟糕的。”他还说，他“只能走一小段距离”，然后就感觉自己“缺氧了”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3760118" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760118" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760118" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic.jpg" alt="大卫·林奇" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/David-Lynch-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Tran_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760118" class="wp-caption-text">大卫·林奇 – 图片来源：Michael Tran/FilmMagic/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>尽管确诊，林奇表示他“永远不会退休”，如果有必要，他将远程指导并从事其他项目。早在六月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-lynch-shares-new-single-and-album-with-chrystabell-3762934">这位</a><i>《双峰》的</i>合著者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-lynch-shares-new-single-and-album-with-chrystabell-3762934">就分享了他最新项目的细节——确认他将与 Chrystabell 发行一张名为“Cellophane Memories”的新专辑</a>。专辑于八月到达。</p><p>林奇和克里斯塔贝尔过去曾合作过，并共同创作了两张专辑。他们还在<i>《双峰：归来》</i>中合作，后者在片中饰演特工塔米·普雷斯顿。</p><p>林奇此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/david-lynch-more-twin-peaks-episodes-storyline-2342534">暗示将回归《<i>双峰》</i>系列</a>，并在 2018 年的签名售会上向粉丝们表示，这个故事“正在召唤，但也存在很多干扰”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-now-requires-supplemental-oxygen-to-walk-its-a-big-price-to-pay-3812940">大卫·林奇现在需要补充氧气才能行走：“这是一个巨大的代价”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
