聆听 Sam Fender 欢快而充满希望的新单曲“People Watching” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sam-fenders-euphoric-and-hopeful-new-single-people-watching-3812916?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-sam-挡泥板-欣快-充满希望-新单身人士观看Surej SinghFri, 15 Nov 2024 01:45:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3812916 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为纪念他已故的朋友和导师而写</p><p>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sam-fenders-euphoric-and-hopeful-new-single-people-watching-3812916">聆听 Sam Fender 欢快而充满希望的新单曲《People Watching》》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sam-fender@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a>发布了他即将发行的专辑《People Watching》的首个官方预览 - 您可以在下面收听。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sam-fender-live-in-newcastle-setlist-photos-3454626">萨姆·芬德在纽卡斯尔现场演出：明星云集的卡通庆祝活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（11 月 15 日），Fender 分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-new-single-people-watching-and-teases-album-news-3810920">即将发行的专辑中的主打歌</a>，该专辑将于 2025 年 2 月 21 日通过 Polydor 发行。您可以<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订黑胶唱片。</p><p>主打单曲《People Watching》是一首欢快的五分钟剪辑，是为了纪念萨姆·芬德已故的导师和朋友安妮·奥尔文而创作的，讲述了他在疗养院探望她的故事。</p><p>与这首歌阴郁的主题并列的是一种明亮、充满希望的声音和信息，概括了走出黑暗时期的过程。他在开场诗中用罂粟吉他和弦唱道：“<em>我在回家的路上看着人们/羡慕一线希望/让我摆脱孤独的感觉/让我有一刻摆脱自我。”</em> ” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：人们观看" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/3ZZyUf7WkhfN1JkQZZ00fI?si=662aa0cdc7db4efc&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>这首歌的第二节更深入地探讨了他对奥尔文的访问：“<em>七年后我回到家/完全清醒，追踪她的眼泪/逼迫护士了解要点/我向她保证我会让她脱离困境疗养院 / 这个地方已经支离破碎 / 人手不足，被冷酷的双手所统治 / 可怜的护士全天候工作 / 青春的美丽已经离开了我破碎的心 / 但当你爱一个人时，这并不难 / 哦， 我彻夜守候，直到你离开此生，因为这就是爱</em>”。</p><p> Fender 上周首次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-people-watching-single-surrogate-mother-to-me-3811192">透露了即将发行的单曲背后的故事</a>，并表示这首歌是关于一个“对我来说就像代孕妈妈一样，于去年 11 月去世的人”的故事。最后我在她身边，睡在她旁边的椅子上。这是关于我脑子里所想的事情，往返于那个地方和家。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这有点讽刺，因为她给了我登上舞台的信心，而且她总是说‘为什么你在获奖感言中没有提到我的名字’。但现在整首歌（和专辑）都与她联系在一起。我希望无论她现在身在何处，她都会低下头说‘是时候了，孩子’。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sam Fender - People Watching（官方专辑预告片）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AaS_CWQ6JJQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《People Watching》标志着 Fender 即将推出的同名专辑的首次正式发行。本周早些时候，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-details-of-new-album-people-watching-3812366">透露了有关该唱片的细节</a>，包括曲目列表。该歌曲由 Fender 与他的乐队成员 Dean Thompson、Joe Atkinson、制作人 Markus Dravs 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-War-on-Drugs">The War on Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 共同制作。</p><p>一份新闻稿将芬德的专辑描述为“他向前迈出的下一步”，承诺提供“丰富多彩的故事和对日常人物日常生活但往往非凡的生活的观察”。</p><p>八月，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-plays-live-debut-for-two-unreleased-songs-people-watching-and-nostalgia-lies-3780786">首次现场演唱了《People Watching》以及另一首未发行的歌曲《Nostalgia&#39;s Lie》</a> ，这两首歌曲都将出现在他期待已久的第三张专辑中。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812392" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812392" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="萨姆·芬德《People Watching》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812392" class="wp-caption-text">萨姆·芬德《People Watching》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>Fender 的上一张专辑《Seventeen Going Under》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-wins-best-album-in-the-world-and-best-album-by-a-uk-artist-bandlab-nme-awards-2022-3172629">在 2022 年 BandLab NME 奖中被评为世界最佳专辑和英国艺术家最佳专辑</a>。 <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">给了它四颗星，称其为“伤痕累累”的第二张专辑</a>，并表示：“如果《Hypersonic Missiles》是一个小男孩向世界踢出的声音，那么《Seventeen Going Under》让 Fender 意识到它可以反击更加困难，他数着每一次打击和擦伤。但他似乎发现，随着时间的推移，大多数伤口——即使是最深的伤口——最终都会愈合，如果他允许的话。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-adds-extra-dates-to-2024-people-watching-uk-and-ireland-dates-3805788">他即将进行的英国和爱尔兰之旅</a>包括在伦敦 O2 音乐厅度过两晚。这些日期售出的每张门票中的 1 英镑将捐赠给音乐场馆信托基金，以支持基层场馆。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsam-fender-tickets%2Fartist%2F5242347" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sam-fenders-euphoric-and-hopeful-new-single-people-watching-3812916">聆听 Sam Fender 欢快而充满希望的新单曲《People Watching》》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
